One more thing.... I was once in a group at level 61 with a level 60 SK.  We were fighting 2 myconid Reavers (level 54-57 or so).  The 60 SK had tank mez'd the Reaver he was on down to about 52% health.  As soon as I got the first reaver killed I switched to the 2nd one, hit auto-attack, and hit taunt.  BOOM, the mob was on me.  This was after the SK had tank mez'd it through a slow and also Darkness'd it.  So taunt definitely (in this situation) did not give me a finite amount of agro on the hate list.... I was no doubt set to the top.  (See the agro stacking thread for more on this)<br>
